Product Description

Printed cotton cambric is a cotton based lightweight plain weave fabric. One of the finest and most dense kinds of cloth, is a lightweight plain-weave cloth, known as batiste. It is used for making dresses and household items.

Applications

Printed cotton cambric fabric, suitable for making dresses, tops, kurti, suits, kaftan, palazzo, kids wear, skirts, blouses and more.
